claim: Flublok ensures identical antigenic match with WHO- and FDA-selected flu strains.
explanation: A CONSORT flow diagram showing participant enrollment, re-enrollment, exclusions, and randomization into different influenza vaccine arms (IIV4, ccIIV4, RIV4) across two study years, with numbers of participants in each re-randomized subgroup. The figure only depicts participant flow and randomization among vaccine groups and provides no information on antigenic composition or match with WHO- or FDA-selected strains, and therefore does not support the claim.
